#

Classic Tomato Basil Pasta Sauce

$5
250 kcal
Difficulty: 30%

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Tags:

SaucePastaItalian

Description

A rich and flavorful tomato sauce with fresh basil, perfect for pasta lovers.

Ingredients

  • Canned Whole Tomatoes: 2 cans (28 oz each)
  • Onion: 1 large, diced
  • Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Olive Oil: 3 tablespoons
  • Fresh Basil: 1 cup, chopped
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
  • Red Pepper Flakes: 1 teaspoon (optional)
